Ash and his friends arrive in Mossgreen Village.
It is a quaint, cute place,
but it is so small it does not even have its own Pokemon Gym.
There is no use stopping here if they do not have a Gym.
- We do not have any choice.
Check out our potion and antidote bag.
I would say this is a good time to stock up on supplies.
Might as well grab a bite to eat, too.
I am dying for a cheeseburger.
I want to eat in a nice restaurant.
Will you two cut it out?

Got some snakeroot that will cure insomnia and grow hair on your nose and tongue.
-Grow hair on your nose and tongue?

I did not mean to scare anyone.
I know, but we are here to help trainers with our miracle potions,

-To unite all peoples within our nation.

This Paras will be your opponent.

The best way for Pokemon to evolve is by winning battles.
The more battles they win, the quicker they evolve.
But what do you want to make Paras evolve so fast for?
Because I have to have Parasect's mushroom.
Why do you need Parasect's mushroom?
I will use its mushroom to make a new potion especially for Pokemon,
and I will use the new potion to help Pokemon all over the world.
She is too terrific to be human.
That is it, I would give up all nine lives to make Cassandra's dream come true.
-He is going to make a fool of himself.
You must think this Cassandra is the cat's Meowth?
I know exactly how you feel about her.
You do not think I am an idiot?
You might say that Cassandra's one female who really knows how to treat a feline.
I was so unprepared for love.
Well, cupid's arrow strikes when you least expect it.
Help me catch, Pikachu, you two lovebird brains.
Just this once, since it is for a good because,
we are going to let Paras win, okay?
All the Pokemon on earth are counting on you.
-Look, Paras is making the first move.

How will Paras ever get any experience?
What am I supposed to do now?

but just enough to sprinkle the mushrooms a little.

Uh, so, what about this potion?
Uh, what is it supposed to do?
Um, I am trying to come up with a miracle potion.

but its attack power, concentration, and its determination as well

When it is done, you should give Ash a taste.
I want all Pokemon to grow and stay healthy.
That is why I need Paras to realize how important it is

then you could become rich beyond your wildest dreams.
Cassandra's miracle Pokemon potion could make millions, maybe even zillions.
And how do we get rich from her potion?
Once me and her are a cozy twosome, she will make me her company mascot.
I was planning on making you two my business managers.
I will have a lot of money to manage.
But if you would rather not, I will understand.
Just imagine, we will have more money than we can count.
I just want to spend the rest of my nine lives
with that trainer of yours, Cassandra.
I can picture it now, her and me sitting on a porch on summer nights.
Who would have thought living with a human could be so purr-fect.
Hurry up, we want to get rich quick.
I cannot do that unless you lend me Arbok and Weezing.
What do you need those two for?
Hmm,because losing battles is their specialty.
They are bigger losers than the guy who invented homework.
How did we get stuck with such rejects?
Now let us bring on our next challenger.
Do not get too much experience.
-Hey, I think it is going to evolve.
Let us see if it is tough enough to defeat me.
A few lousy wins and it thinks it is Tarzan.
Maybe they can help us get Paras to evolve.
How did it get up in that tree?
I have never seen it act like this before.
Maybe it is Paras' sparring partner.
Oh, Paras, you finally understand my dream.
Pikachu, it is time to help Paras evolve into Parasect.
My plan is going to work.
Remember, Pikachu, go easy on it.
If you keep battling it like this,
then Paras is almost sure to gain enough experience to evolve into Parasect.
Charmeleon, I am counting on you this time.
If the trainer is poor, the Pokemon will not respect him and will not obey orders.
I got to do something to help Paras win.

We are the official Pokemon pep squad, here to cheer on our hero.
Paras, do not forget all the training we gave you.
-There is no way you can lose.
Give a cheer for our ace, the great Paras!
Char, char, char, char, char, char.
Parasect, the mushroom Pokemon, it battles using poison spheres
that spread from the mushroom canopy on its back.
We are all proud of you, Parasect.

it will definitely make a powerful potion.

Next time I will be fine.
I knew I would be able to count on you.

I am going to make my miracle potion

I will be your first customer.
Good luck on your journey, everyone.
And just as Ash and friends are saying goodbye,
I got to be the luckiest cat in the entire universe.
who went from chump to champ in record-breaking time.
How can we ever repay you?
Thanks to you, we will make the greatest potion ever known.
It was nothing after you cooled me off, it was the least I could do.

I guess it is only natural to make me your company mascot-
I would never tear you away from Team Rocket.
